). Total 4 of 167 patients (2.4%) showed structural defects related to HCQ (Table 2
). On VFA 30–2, of 167 patients, 159 (95.2%) patients did not have any features suggestive of HCQ retinopathy, 8 (4.8%) patients had VFA based HCQ retinopathy (Table 3
